dcterms:description: This dataset consists of recordings of electroencephalography (EEG), electrooculography (EOG), and electromyography (EMG) used for sleep stage classification, detecting five sleep stages: Awake, Stage 1 (S1), Stage 2 (S2), Slow wave sleep (SWS), and Rapid eye movement (REM).

dcterms:description: This dataset includes polysomnogram records from five males and females, used for sleep stage classification into five stages: Awake, Stage 1 (S1), Stage 2 (S2), Stage 3 (S3), and Rapid eye movement (REM). The data annotation was performed by a sleep specialist.
dcterms:title: Mitra Keluarga Kemayoran Dataset
